🍦Yummiest scent from KAYALI 🍨! Was super excited to receive this Yum Pistachio Gelato 33 from kayali and skeepers_us 💚 TYSM!😘

Key Notes: 
Pistachio Gelato
Hazelnut 
Sweet Rum 
Whipped Cream 
Marshmallow 
Cotton Candy 

One spray is enough to experience this yummy fragrance. Tbh I didn’t know what to expect from a ‘Pistachio’ scent, but this one is a keeper! It’s delicious but not overly sweet, dries down to a fresh powdery scent with a hint of the sweetness. I don’t usually go for sweet scents but this has the right balance and not overpowering. Too strong scents trigger my rhinitis but not this. 

Beautiful unique scent added to my small fragrance collection. Recently bought a perfume at Sephora (famous brand) but then my husband said I smell like everyone else at the mall🤣. Let’s just say I won’t smell like majority of the people when I wear this perfume. It’s been 9 hours since i sprayed it on me and i can still smell it although faint now. I could see myself wearing this day or night and perfect this spring!

What is your fave fragrance this spring?🌸

Fenty 
fentybeauty 

blueberry citrus 
velvet bulgarian rose 
they’ll shine together 

Rihanna, the best smelling celebrity. It’s no wonder she hit it out of the park with her own perfume. This is a sultry, warm, addictive fragrance created entirely of heart notes. The Fenty website lists magnolia, musk, tangerine, and Bulgarian rose as the primary notes. And there’s blueberry, geranium, coconut, patchouli, and vanilla coming together to create something - described by master perfumer Jacques Cavalier - as alluring and dynamic as Rihanna herself. 

If it rained Fenty I wouldn’t stand under my umbrella.

¡Buenas noches! ✨

Hoy vengo a hablaros de una paleta que probablemente la mayoría ya conozcáis, porque en su momento se puso muy de moda cuando salió al mercado 🥹 Se trata de la paleta Rose Quartz de hudabeauty 💘 Yo me resistía a hacerme con ella pero la conseguí rebajadisima en sephora (me parece que a 45 euros estaba 😱) y no me pude aguantar más 🙊

Os cuento un poco: 

Es una paleta inspirada en la piedra favorita de Huda, el cuarzo rosa 💖 Está compuesta por 18 sombras en diferentes acabados: 

✨ 8 tonos mate ✨
✨3 tonos metálicos ultrabrillantes✨
✨3 tonos metalizados perlados✨
✨ 3 tonos en crema veteados✨
✨ 1 tono hibrido (el de bolitas que no le gusta a nadie 😅)✨

Si deslizáis podeis ver todos los tonos ( he intentado hacer swatches decentes 🫶🏻🤣), como podéis ver la pigmentación es increíble y es que las sombras se difuminan como la mantequilla y tienen una duración brutal 💖 Nunca había tenido una paleta grande de Huda y estoy encantadisima porque puedes hacer looks más diarios y luego utilizar algunos de los tonos metalizados para hacer algo más potente 🤩

Estoy gratamente sorprendida con la calidad de esta paleta y, aunque algunos tonos no van mucho conmigo (el de las bolitas 😢) me parece que es una paleta muy completa y que le podria encajar a cualquiera 💖

La tenéis disponible en sephora_spain a un precio de 70€ pero la he visto muchas veces con descuentos grandes como el mio, así que si la veis corred 🏃🏻‍♀️🤣 Ah! Y obviamente también está en la propia web de hudabeauty 

Contadme, ¿la habéis probado? ¿Tenéis paletas de Huda Beauty? ¡Os leo! 🙈

Jesteśmy bardzo zadowoleni z używania tego kremu, i trafia on na listę tych kosmetyków, do których z chęcią wrócimy, na pewno latem.

J’ai lu ce livre en une journée. 

Beaucoup plus poétique que Tu peux toujours courir, l’histoire n’est pas sans péripéties. Vascillant entre les proses et les poèmes, la narratrice nous trainent dans sa petite vie tantôt sereine tantôt périlleuse. J’ai adoré la lecture surtout pour les jeux de mots et le côté poétique de l’histoire. 

Étrangement, certains passages m’ont rendu nostalgique du premier confinement covidien. 

Une belle lecture à avoir lors d’une journée tempête, réfugié.e dans une couverture chaude et buvant un bon chocolat chaud.

🔆 𝗬𝘂𝗺 𝗣𝗶𝘀𝘁𝗮𝗰𝗵𝗶𝗼 𝗚𝗲𝗹𝗮𝘁𝗼 | 𝟯𝟯 𝗞𝗮𝘆𝗮𝗹𝗶

Newest launch by KAYALI Fragrances. A very fresh delightful, enticing scent, where the notes of Pistachio, Bergamot, Pear, white Peach, Cotton Candy, Loukhoum, Sandalwood and Tonka Bean stand out.

On my skin this vivacious aroma, fruity and sparkling evokes what a yummy pistachio sorbet is; I conceive it as a gourmand ideal for spring and summertime; opening with Pear, Pistachio, adding the citrusy Bergamot. The dry down is sugary and the particular nutty nuances really shine. Sillage is moderate to wide. The projection for the first few hours is excellent, it lasts a total of 5-7 hours on my skin.

I must applaud the creativity of the perfumers in charge, Olivier and Sebastien Cresp. It is unlike anything I have tried before and it has the potential to be a hit - especially for the younger audiences and above all for yummy sweet dessert lovers- like me!

It may be unisex, but I find it feminine leaning. It’s bright. It’s sweet like candy! It’s like eating ice cream outside in the summertime. Have you already tried it? Share your experience below.

Eau de Parfum Available formats of 10, 50 and 100 ml. 🏷️ kayali 

🇪🇸 Nueva oferta Gourmand de la casa KAYALI. En mi caso particular resulta una fragancia muy fresca, apetecible en todo caso, donde se destacan las notas de Pistacho, Bergamota, Pera, Melocotón blanco, Algodón de Azúcar, Sándalo y Haba Tonka. En mi piel este un aroma vivaracho, chispeante frutal, me evoca a lo que es un sorbete de pistacho; lo concibo como un Gourmand para primavera y verano; el pistacho se une a la pera, sumándole la cítrica bergamota de salida. En el secado emanan toques azucarados, frescos y amaderados.

Cabe destacar la creatividad de los perfumistas a cargo, Olivier y Sebastien Cresp en esta oferta. Es un perfume que no se asemeja a nada que haya probado hasta el momento y lo siento como un hit para el público juvenil y sobre todo les estará haciendo ojitos a los amantes de los aromas gourmands, ¡como yo!

Корейские палетки - моя особая слабость. 

И тут у меня две палетки бренда IPKN из серии "Season Color Eye Palette". Первая  в раскладке My Day Blush.

Мой дневной румянец выглядит очень свежо и нюдово. В эту палетку я сразу запустила пальчики, я обожаю корейские тени в использовании. Это как и ежеденевное простое и быстрое, так и отличные тушевочные оттенки. Если не хочется думать - беру корейские тени. Названия у оттенков нет, зато есть классическая номерация слева направо. 
В палетке 6 оттенков, 4 из которых матовые.

Начну по привычки с матовых: оттенки 3 и 4 - матовые, но с вкрапление цветного шиммера. В 3 оттенке серебристый шиммер, в 4м - розовый. Суховатые, пигментация средняя. 
Оттенки 5 и 6 просто матовые, пигментация выше среднего.

Оттенок 1 - спаркл, чтоб показать его на фото пришлось наслаиваться, дабы показать розовый перелив, шиммер в нем розовые и желтые разных размеров, красивый.
Оттенок 2 - шиммер, дуохромит в нежно розовый, есть синие вкрапления. Также пришлось понизить экспозицию ,чтоб показать какое свечение. 
Тени хорошо тушуются, красиво сияют на глазах, особенно при разном освещении - мне кажется это фишечка оттенков 1 и 2.

It’s amazing what a little lip filler can do — 😘
•
Slowly building a thinner lip is important to allow for the tissue to have time to expand and settle before adding more 
•
She has had her lips done in the past & felt as if she had lack of shape and some migration due to overfilling what the lip could handle in a single session 
•
We will continue to slowly build them over time but are thrilled with the volume and shape we were able to get after starting with a fresh base ✨
•

#HdMFeatures Hu Weiyi⁠
⁠
In depth research and an interest in experimental film and theatrical performance imbue hu_weiyi  multimedia experiments, which he uses to open new avenues for social ethnography, both as artist and curator. Working in photography, video and installation he is a resourceful montage artist. A series called Flirt introduced cold light to various objects to manipulate a viewer’s perception of them, an effect he achieved without resorting to digital software manipulation. In his Window Blind series of installations, screens display videos of apartment blocks in Chinese residential buildings.

Born in 1990 in Shanghai, Weiyi’s work has been exhibited or collected by major museums and art centres, including k11artfoundation xmuseum_official #helmhauszuerich yuzmuseum powerstationofart thelongmuseum mocashanghai timesmuseum minsheng_art_museum cafaartmuseum

I bought this 'Glow Recipe' pack from sephora and wanted to try it as I saw a lot of positive reviews. I'm using it in my PM skin routine. You can use it in AM or PM both. It's totally up to you.

Set includes: PHA + BHA pore-tight toner, Niacinamide dew drops, Hyaluronic serum, Pink juice moisturiser, and Avocado retinol eye cream.

The price for this pack on sale was SR138
Their pack offers usually change with time to time, so you have to keep checking. Otherwise, single products are available. Prices are according to the size.

✔️ PROS
✨️ This really brings glow to your face.
✨️ You will feel your skin so soft and smooth.
✨️ Make sure you wash your face properly before using it, and then the result is awesome.
✨️ It's instructed to use one pump, and trust me, one pump is far enough.
✨️ Its niacinamide dew drops could be used as a primer,could be mixed with foundation, could be used as a highlighter, or on your eyes for a natural glow.
✨️ I use niacinamide serum's one pump with one pump of pink juice moisturiser, and it gives mind-blowing results.
✨️ When I don't want to do any make-up, I can simply go with these products on.

❌️ CONS
There are no serious cons so far, but one thing you have to be careful about is the amount you use. Only one pump is usually enough. Too much product might break out your skin, especially if you have acne prone skin or sensitive skin.
My skin also breaks out easily, but while I'm using these products, nothing like this happened with me.

🔸️ My Rating: 10/10

💕FOUNDATION SPEED REVIEWS💕

💕 1. Sephora Best Skin Ever foundation: is said to be medium coverage, natural finish, longwearing, anti-pollution formula that hydrates skin for 12 hours. Contained Hyaluronic acid (hydrates), Red Algae extract (hydrates) & Brown Algae extract (provides anti pollution protective shield. 

I know a lot of MUAs like to use this foundation for its color range + the benefits mentioned above. 

REVIEW: this foundation was ok. I felt it never died down and it would smudge unless I heavily set it with powder. Would not purchase again. 

💕2. Ulta Beauty Complexion Crush in Light•Medium: super blendable, lightweight foundation blurs skin texture, evens skin tone yet feels lightweight and skin looks fresh even after setting with powder. 

REVIEW: I love this foundation!! It does blur and skin looks natural & healthy. This makes for a perfect winter foundation here in Florida. 

💕3. Neutrogena Healthy Skin foundation SPF 55: a flawless, natural look and protection against the sun's damaging rays with Neutrogena Healthy Skin Compact Makeup Broad Spectrum SPF 55. This silky, lightweight makeup provides buildable coverage. With Broad Spectrum SPF 55, this formula also helps provide the most powerful level of UVA/UVB protection available in a compact foundation without feeling heavy or greasy. When used as directed along with other sun protection measures, it helps prevent sunburn, and decreases the risk of skin cancer and early skin aging caused by the sun. This dermatologist-tested formula is non-comedogenic which means it won't clog pores. Plus, this cream foundation contains vitamins A, B5, C, and E. 

REVIEW: this foundation looks pretty on the skin yet needs to be set with powder or else it wears off quickly. It looks pretty at first as long as skin prep is done. Gives off flashback. I don’t feel it’s worth it for the price since this finished fast compared to liquid foundations.

#firstaidbeautygiftedme Almohadillas de un solo uso que exfolian suavemente la piel para eliminar las células muertas de la piel que atrapan el vello, lo que ayuda a prevenir la formación de quemaduras por afeitado y bultos encarnados dolorosos.
Ideales para usar en áreas como axilas, entre pierna o pubis después de la depilación.
Segura para pieles sensibles, la fórmula con Witch Hazel y Aloe deja la piel suave y tersa.

FAB  Ingredientes :
- Ácido Glicólico: Exfolia y renueva visiblemente la piel.
- Ácido salicílico: ilumina visiblemente, suaviza la textura y purifica.
- Hamamelis: Calma la piel.

Cómo utilizar:
-Pase una almohadilla sobre la piel limpia y seca todos los días.
-Empezar a usar un día después del afeitado o depilación.
-Se puede usar en las axilas, el área del bikini, la cara/cuello, las piernas y en cualquier otro lugar donde se elimine el vello.

🫧🤍💚 Yum Pistachio Gelato 33 💚🤍🫧 by kayali ✨ my thoughts 💗 ⬇️

Initial Impression: I love it! 💖 It’s hands down my favorite Kayali fragrance now 🙌🏼 
It’s soothing & sweet, it’s different from what I had in mind. I had high expectations, but honestly this fragrance surpassed my expectation. 
I was expecting a gourmand ice cream fragrance, but It’s  like giving ‘worlds most expensive icey gelato 🍧 at a garden’
it’s a gooey sweet upbeat citrusy fragrance w a hint of wood

✨The opening is citrusy but also sweet. I pick up on heavy bergamot, smooth rum, and icey gelato 💚

✨Around 10 mins in, the jasmine germanium and raspberry come through. It’s like walking through a garden with sweets. 🍨🪷💗
As the fragrance sits it starts to sweeten up more 

✨ Then the base notes settle in I get balanced whipped cream, chocolatey tonka, marshmallow, a touch of citrus & wood 🤍

🫧🪷🌿 A marvelous spring fragrance 🌿🪷🫧

( update: it’s beautiful ✨ it did hold up on me personally for 3 hours. However, to push the longevity I layered it with other scents, with which this fragrance did shine through and preformed beautifully. I need another bottle asap so I can overspray✨)

✨ Full List of the Scent Notes:
Bergamont, Pistachio Gelato, Hazelnut, Rum, Cardamom, Germanium, White Peony, Muguet, Jasmine, Raspberry, White Peach, Pear, Whipped Cream, Marshmallow, Cotton Candy, Turkish Delight Accord, Cocoa, Cedarwood, Sandalwood, Tonka
